data.description: Experience the best of Lake Oswego living in this beautifully designed one level condo in an elevator-served building. From the moment you step inside, you'll be struck by the thoughtful touches that make this home truly exceptional. Gorgeous hardwood floors span the unit, while plentiful storage space ensures that everything you need is always within reach. The spacious bedrooms, featuring luxurious walk-in closets, updated bathrooms, and mini-split systems ensuring you always have the perfect temperature. A beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, new stainless-steel appliances, and an abundance of cabinet space for all your cooking essentials. The living room features a wood-burning fireplace, creating a cozy atmosphere.  When it's time to unwind, step out into the sunroom and take in all the serene views. With a detached 1-car garage and access to Mountain Park's impressive amenities, including a pool, recreation center, and scenic walking trails, you'll have everything you need to live your best life in Lake Oswego. Don't miss your chance to make this gorgeous condo your new home.
